{"fadein":1.5,"once":true,"id":"JUNHEBOSS3","fadeType":2,"mode":2,"fadeOut":1.5,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"sequence":[["Crosswave\n\n<size=45>A Leader's Prowess<\/size>",1]],"stopbgm":true},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":2,"bgm":"cw-story","say":"Port - Exercise Area","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"bgmDelay":2,"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1]}},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"action":[{"number":2,"x":0,"type":"shake","delay":0,"dur":0.15,"y":30}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"They got meeeee!","actor":301160},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":4,"dir":1,"say":"Another dead end... Yukikaze, fall back to our line of defense! Taihou and I will cover you!","actor":900200},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":2,"dir":1,"say":"You certainly know how to work someone hard... Yukikaze, now!","actor":307070},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Understood! ... I mean, consider yourselves off the hook for now!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301160},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1]},"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":4,"dir":1,"say":"Somehow, we managed to fend off the Commander's onslaught... But as the battle gets drawn out, we'll surely get whittled down...","actor":900200},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Grrr... How is it possible that not even Yukikaze the Great could put a halt to the Commander's fleet...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301160},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":3,"dir":1,"say":"It seems we're at a loss. We can adjust our strategy all we want, but Commander's fleet seems to always be a step ahead of us.","actor":307070},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"There are Eagle Union ships that have managed it before, you know...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301160},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"And, while I wouldn't mind suffering a crushing defeat at my Commander's hands, that would reflect poorly on the Sakura Empire's reputation...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307070},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":4,"dir":1,"say":"I'll admit, one's motivation starts to diminish when a battle feels as one-sided as this... Having said that, we must not resort to using cheap tricks, like Yukikaze said...","actor":900200},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":3,"dir":1,"say":"......","actor":900200},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"They're forcing my hand...!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900200},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"nameColor":"#a9f548","flashout":{"black":true,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1]},"dir":1,"say":"Taihou, Yukikaze, please listen. I have an idea for how we can turn this around.","actor":900200},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"But how? And let me just get this out of the way; I might be lucky, but even I can't magically triple our fleet power!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301160},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":1,"dir":1,"say":"There's still a way for us to get the upper hand in this situation?","actor":307070},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Yes. By ignoring all the other opponents and going straight for the Commander.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900200},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"No way! Not even Yukikaze the Great could plow through to the center of that massive fleet...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301160},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":1,"dir":1,"say":"You won't be alone. We'll bait the ship the Commander is on to come here, then attack all at once.","actor":900200},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":1,"dir":1,"say":"It doesn't matter if you use cannons or bombs, just take out that flagship! Got it?","actor":900200},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"But how do you know where the Commander is?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307070},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":3,"dir":1,"say":"Why, I thought you of all people would know, Taihou... Would you mind doing some recon for us?","actor":900200},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":5,"dir":1,"say":"Me?! ... Need I even answer that question? I would absolutely love to locate the Commander!","actor":307070},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","expression":2,"dir":1,"say":"Appreciate it. I'll give you specific instructions later, so for now just try not to let the Commander catch wind of our plan.","actor":900200},{"bgName":"bg_story_nepu2","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"blackBg":true,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Set sail!","actor":900200}]}